{"tid":1475934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"818 遊行完去邊度?","createTime":"2019-08-15T15:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T13:46:06.000Z","uid":55130,"like":23,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d28267c4fe7ccb2968c5339e8454b0a3026533","tid":1475934,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"唔係圍政總 唔係圍狗總 唔係圍支聯辨 唔係圍禮賓府<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我自己係會入機場</span></span><br />\n最近我係度諗緊 到底呢場運動要點行落去<br />\n侵考慮出手 之後呢?<br />\n假手於人去得到民主 係唔係我地想要?<br />\n如果係咁 到最後我地都係奶其他國家既屎眼去生存<br />\n我地係應該要自己去爭取 用自己雙手去攞番自己既尊嚴<br />\n呢個係屬於我地既時代<br />\n<br />\n我地要係呢場運動 甚至革命入面 <br />\n揸住林奠個春袋去攞番我地失去既野<br />\n親手去收港共皮 去收共產黨皮<br />\n<br />\n入正題 其實小弟我毒丁一個 唔太識路去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁果日行去遮打就完<br />\n咁最正路就係機鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uKnG4f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuKnG4f4.jpg&h=10c07369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係 呢一日有機會100萬人 太多人搭黨鐵<br />\n港島行車線應該收埋皮 A11多數無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他地區巴士路線太多 唔提啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就諗住用PLAN B由東涌入行去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WZpyaYH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZpyaYH.png&h=e2b92075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時想係機場識下唔同國藉既女女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我會帶埋野食邀請佢地一齊露營<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知有無巴打到時想一齊交換下野食呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n人渣黑狗 以眼還眼<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef313d1d1cd126f31f762ecef2ff99c42172925","tid":1475934,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:50:22.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fb21485a374c1eec5cdf235677321678da6e6aa1","tid":1475934,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3JRwHeE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3JRwHeE.jpg&h=f866eeef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b28c041d416e50586507b54bdf97ae152c9a721","tid":1475934,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjCPtUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjCPtUU.jpg&h=ba57287b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3fa2f4d37a5d7e68659d581577fdde0fa6de755","tid":1475934,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yL8SrGG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyL8SrGG.jpg&h=aededbcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a307040d6a95fd4f656d1c2073e897560be934c6","tid":1475934,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AcPutVb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAcPutVb.jpg&h=e51b0aaa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cfdec207438e257c625c34361df7cf1cb66f663","tid":1475934,"uid":279763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb21485a374c1eec5cdf235677321678da6e6aa1","tid":1475934,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3JRwHeE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/